{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"92cfb62b96","title":"关于缩减在辽东等地修建国防工事计划的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f3bd76fed4","index":0,"year":1953,"month":7,"day":11,"articleId":"92cfb62b96"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"794b6f1c7a","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"92cfb62b96","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"黄克诚，当时任中国人民解放军副总参谋长。"},{"id":"6cffa6fa48","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"92cfb62b96","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指黄克诚1953年7月11日给毛泽东的报告中提出的缩减在辽东等地修建国防工事的计划。报告中说，鉴于各种条件的限制，如财力、物力、技术、技术领导均缺乏，领导干部和施工部队又无近代筑城经验，5年完成原计划确有很大困难。因此，拟对整个计划重新研究一下，采取稳步修建的方针，即前3年少修，求得锻炼干部，取得经验后再逐年增加。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2de61c6709","type":"title","text":"关于缩减在辽东等地修建国防工事计划的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"92cfb62b96"},{"id":"794b6f1c7a","type":"paragraph","text":"黄克诚同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"92cfb62b96"},{"id":"6cffa6fa48","type":"paragraph","text":"赞成你的缩减计划，这是很必要的，望照此部署","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"92cfb62b96"},{"id":"a03e81bca8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"92cfb62b96"},{"id":"805102c7ea","type":"paragraph","text":"七月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"92cfb62b96"}],"page":{"id":"af7355de5b","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"92cfb62b96","start":242,"end":242}}}},"__N_SSG":true}